title: Kiss - Discography Mastered for iTunes 2014 [MP3 320kbps]
description:
This is the BEST the Kiss discography has ever sounded! The engineers at iTunes did a great job remastering the Kiss catalog. Every album now has a bit more bass presence, and overall has a more tight crisp feel. All of this was done without clipping or heavy compression (most songs range from DR8 - DR10).

Please note the albums MTV Unplugged (1996), Psycho Circus (1998), Alive Symphony (2003) Sonic Boom (2009) and Monster (2012) were not remastered by iTunes for Kiss's 40 year celebration, so they are not included.

Also, I've spent a lot of time to make this torrent, because I think everyone deserves to hear KISS at their BEST! And it's also cost me $150 to buy all the music, so if you enjoy this please SEED and give a thumbs or comment!
